<%- include("./../partials/header.ejs") %>

<div class="container about-container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="about-title mb-4">About Alhamad Relocations</h1>
            <p class="lead about-intro">
                Welcome to <strong>Alhamad Relocations</strong>, your smart and convenient solution to manage and label your moving boxes.
                Here’s how our platform works to make your moving experience organized and hassle-free.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">Account Features</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li><strong>Create an Account:</strong> Sign up with your email or log in with Google for quick access.</li>
                <li><strong>Account Verification:</strong> Verify your email after sign-up to activate your account.</li>
                <li><strong>Profile Management:</strong> Update your profile picture, change your password, or deactivate/activate your account anytime.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">Label Management</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li><strong>Create a Label:</strong> Choose a label design, name it, and decide if it’s public or private.</li>
                <li><strong>Data Upload:</strong> Upload images, text, or audio to your label for more detailed information.</li>
                <li><strong>Public vs. Private Labels:</strong> Public labels can be shared, while private labels require a 6-digit code to view when scanned.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">Label Actions</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li><strong>View Your Labels:</strong> Manage your labels, edit, delete, or share them from the Labels page.</li>
                <li><strong>Shared Labels:</strong> Find labels shared with you in the Shared Labels section.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
            <h2 class="section-title">Print and Organize</h2>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li><strong>Print Labels:</strong> Print your labels and attach them to your moving boxes.</li>
                <li><strong>QR Code:</strong> Each label includes a unique QR code to view the contents. Private labels require a 6-digit code to access.</li>
                <li><strong>Organized Boxes:</strong> Make moving easier by providing movers with a clear idea of the contents, ensuring careful handling of your boxes.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5 text-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
            <h3 class="about-thank-you">Thank you for choosing <strong>Alhamad Relocations</strong>!</h3>
            <p class="lead">We hope our platform makes your move stress-free and more organized.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

